91
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:59,634
Lord Winchelsea.

92
00:16:00,769 --> 00:16:02,532
Lord Orlando.

93
00:16:03,872 --> 00:16:07,672
- El conde de Moray.
- Moray. Teasle.

94
00:16:07,743 --> 00:16:10,507
